reviewText:
I managed a whole 3 minutes on this game, that consisted of;

-     change settings to playable mode"
-     open help menu which turns out to be unreadable

Amazingly boring. DO NOT BUY THIS GAME... As already mentioned, do not even accept it as a gift. I have read the comments too late, unfortunately. As it is never enough:

- Plane arrives (takes a while);
- You drive every vehicle to the plane (takes another while, depending on gate;
- You wait a load of time listening to the same loop music... Sanity check here;
- You drive everything back to the respective garage;
- You upgrade (hire assistants - no more driving) everything.

That`s all. After a while you will probably upgrade everything and win the game (I have not survived more than 30 minutes, so I have no idea of what would be this end").

Can STEAM refund? lol

